{
  "id": "69f7c020cbc07b2646278d94",
  "title": "2026/03/28―nishio",
  "created": 1777844258,
  "updated": 1777844421,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f7c020cbc07b2646278d94",
      "text": "2026/03/28―nishio",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b3",
      "text": "from [2026/03/28]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844261
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b5",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b6",
      "text": "　> [@umekkii https://twitter.com/umekkii/status/2037469336097726554]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b7",
      "text": " > 一審で勝訴して二審敗訴で話題になった事件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b8",
      "text": " > 最高裁が５人全員一致での逆転勝訴ということで、気になって判決読んでみたら、形式的に法を適用するんじゃなくて現実を見ろというめっちゃ熱い思い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192b9",
      "text": " > 補足意見では更に思いが滲んでて面白い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192ba",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192bb",
      "text": " > https://www.courts.go.jp/hanrei/95768/detail2/index.html ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192bc",
      "text": " > > [@nikkei https://twitter.com/nikkei/status/2037413639980720290]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192bd",
      "text": " > > [猟銃許可取り消し「違法」、クマ駆除のハンター逆転勝訴　最高裁判決 https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUD212D80R20C26A3000000/]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192be",
      "text": "　　判決文読んだ、面白かった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192bf",
      "text": "　[https://gyazo.com/809ef4dd9d166339340706b2f9688ff4]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c0",
      "text": "　　全部「真実」だw 面白い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c1",
      "text": "　　「AはB」形式を繰り返したらパターン認識でそれっぽく見えるのだろうか[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c2",
      "text": "　　「小泉進次郎の支持基盤は半島」は面白い[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c3",
      "text": " 　　[https://gyazo.com/8d39fdc96512e3fcfe14fc41e20fff4b]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c4",
      "text": " 　　思った以上に半島してる半島だった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c5",
      "text": " 　　房総半島とかかと思ったけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c6",
      "text": " 　　\tちなみに房総半島は川で切断されていたはず。島やん。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c7",
      "text": " 　　\t　それな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c8",
      "text": " 　　\t　他にもそういうエリアあんのかな[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192c9",
      "text": "  　　\t　珍しくはありそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192ca",
      "text": "  　　\t　条件",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192cb",
      "text": "  　　\t　\t川の枝分かれ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192cc",
      "text": "  　　\t　\t2つの川の水源が一致しているパターン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192cd",
      "text": "  　　\t　関連: [分水嶺]・水分かれ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192ce",
      "text": "  　　\t　中洲やデルタ、つまり　分岐のち合流　というパターンは、島というふうにとらえやすい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192cf",
      "text": " 　　\t江戸川と利根川で切断されている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d0",
      "text": " 　　\t\t熊の生息域の話で、露骨に房総半島だけ事件件数が少ないみたいな話があった。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d1",
      "text": " 　　\t\t[https://mainichi.jp/maisho/articles/20240130/kei/00s/00s/015000c 毎日小学生新聞]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d2",
      "text": " 　　\t\t事件件数が少ないどころか史上熊の記録が一切ない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d3",
      "text": "　論点を整理してたら個人のリスク許容度の話になり、僕個人のリスク許容度は一般的な分布から外れてるので自分の考えを一般的なもののように言ってはいけないな、という気持ちが強くなってしまった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d4",
      "text": "　　何も言えなくなるw",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d5",
      "text": "　　僕みたいに[株式を担保に金を借りて株式を買う]「二階建て」をやる人は間違いなく少数派なので参考にしてはいけないw",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d6",
      "text": "　[井戸端のムーブメント]にキャッチアップできてないw",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d7",
      "text": "　 何がバチバチしてたのかもよくわかってないが、まあこれはキャッチアップする必要ないかと思ってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d8",
      "text": "　  同じく[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192d9",
      "text": "　 個人日記を個人のCosenseプロジェクトに置くのと、井戸端に置くのではなんらかの違いがありそうで、実験として興味深い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192da",
      "text": "　 先日僕が日記冒頭部につらつらとまとまってない思考を書き連ねたときにこの個人日記の発想があればそれを選択してた気がする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844258
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c02100000000007192db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844258,
      "updated": 1777844416
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f012b",
      "text": "from [2026/03/28]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f012c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f012d",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f012e",
      "text": "　礼服を作り直すミッション✅",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f012f",
      "text": "　韓国語は「ちんちゃましそよ」しか知らない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f0130",
      "text": "　　嘘だった、「さらんへよ」も知ってるわ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f0131",
      "text": "　　あんにょんはせよ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f0132",
      "text": "　　\tかむさへよ / かむさはむにだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0b900000000005f0133",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844410,
      "updated": 1777844410
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0bc00000000005f0134",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844412,
      "updated": 1777844412
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c0bc00000000005f0135",
      "text": "[2026/05/04 お試し個別日記を作成]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777844412,
      "updated": 1777844412
    },
